@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Lấy danh sách món ăn cho Bếp (Get Kitchen Items)

actor "Đầu bếp (Dashboard UI)" as Chef
participant "ChefController" as Ctrl
participant "OrderService" as Svc
participant "OrderDetailRepository" as Repo
database "Database" as DB

Chef -> Ctrl : GET /chef/api/items
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> Svc : getKitchenOrders()
activate Svc

Svc -> Repo : findByServedStatusInOrderByOrderDetailIdAsc([PENDING, COOKING])
activate Repo

Repo -> DB : SELECT * FROM order_details WHERE served_status IN (...)
DB --> Repo : List<OrderDetail>
deactivate Repo

Svc -> Svc : Lọc các OrderDetail có Order != null
Svc --> Ctrl : List<OrderDetail> (Sạch)
deactivate Svc

Ctrl -> Ctrl : Nhóm món ăn theo OrderId (groupingBy)
Ctrl -> Ctrl : Chuyển đổi sang Map<String, Object> (JSON format)
note right: Bao gồm thông tin Bàn,\nTên món, Số lượng, Ghi chú

Ctrl --> Chef : List of Order Maps
deactivate Ctrl

@enduml